DataElement.preferredName: Neoplastic Cell Folate Receptor Alpha Staining Additive Percentage Value
DataElement.preferredDefinition: Additive value of Percentage of tumor cells with membrane and cytoplasmic staining for Folate Receptor Alpha expression based on staining intensity (1+, 2+, 3+).    The value is B+C+D where B=% of cells with 1+ positive staining, and C= %of cells with 2+ positive staining, and D= %of cells with 3+ positive staining.
